title: Hour 1: William Shatner
description:
Jason Kelce's comments spark a conversation about white cornerbacks, we dive back into why NFL owners hate Dan Snyder, and the show may have been wrong about Joe Musgrove. Then, Google has made us dumb, a legendary Kirk Ferentz quote, and why Let Russ Cook has turned into Let Geno Cook. Plus, William Shatner joins the show!
